      "content": "wait wait, if I take insulin now while my sugar is low, won't that make it even lower? i'm a bit confused. i thought insulin was the standard for when things feel off. if i feel like i'm crashing, isn't it safer to just take a small amount to keep everything stable? i don't want to risk a massive spike later if i'm actually high.",
